history.text: Do you like superhero movies, you should watch Wonder Woman.
I actually love superhero movies. Are you talking about the new Wonder Woman movie?
Yes, the one with Gal Gadot. Patty Jenkins did great as director.
Really? What is about other than Wonder Woman?
I'm not sure. I really liked Diana's action scenes and how she used love to fight war.

Wait,
 who is Diana?
Diana Prince is Wonder Woman. I really liked the scenes on her home islanad of Themyscria.
What is her home island like?
It is a hidden island, home to the Amazononinwarrior
Also, since this is a superhero movie who is the main villain in the movie?
Ares became jealous of humanity and wants to kill all of mankind.
Where is Ares from?
I'm not sure. Do you like these kinds of movies? I especially enjoyed the scenes between Steve and Diana, like when she used the Lasso of Hestia.
I do like these types of movies, but who is Steve?
Did you watch this movie? Steve is the American Pilot that crashed on Diana's island.
No I didn't
i am trying to decide if I want to watch it.
This movie seems to have a lot going on, how long is it?
I can't remember. It is pretty straight forward. Diana took the Godkiller sword to defeat Ares, that was fun.
Sounds like there is plenty of action in this movie. Are there any cameos from other superheros?
Well the movie is mostly about Diana versus Ares. That battle was intense. The scene with Steve saving the world was sad too.
How does Steve save the world?

He takes a plane full of gas into high altitude 
so that it detonates without killing people, sacrificing himself.
What's the relationship between Steve and Wonder Woman?
His death gave her a lot of grief and caused her to use her rage on Ares. She saw good in him. Obviously she liked him a lot.
I was wondering if it was romantic or not
This movie is more about the story of Wonder Woman.

uid2response.feedback: I wasn't provided a document to read. My chat partner took a while to respond to questions,  and their answers were fairly vague, however, I will still go watch the movie based on some of the storyline plots I got from the conversation.
